<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē saptarāmatriśaśiparimitē māsi vaiśākha saṁjñē pakṣē śu
<lb n="2" break="no"/>klē tṛtīyēhani naraharayē kāvyavārē pradīpaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> prādādācaṁdratāraṁ ha
<lb n="3" break="no"/>giripatayēkhaṁḍamiṣṭārttasiddyai <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīmānvatsānvavāyī lakhavuvarasutō
<lb n="4"/>ghugghulurnnāyakāgryaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1337 gunēṁṭi vaiśākha
<lb n="5"/>śuddha tṛ<supplied reason="omitted">tī</supplied>ya śukravāramunaḍu rāyapurana ḍahāḷa lakhavunāyani ko
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḍuku ghughghulunāIyaṁḍu tanakunu Iṣṭārttasiddigānu sihyādrināthu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ni saṁmukhamaṁdunu nityamunnu veluṁguṭakunu Akhaṁḍadīpa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>mu pratimasaItamuganu peṭṭanu Idula samarunakai kilari śrī
<lb n="9" break="no"/>patisēnavati koḍuku kanakadharavaradusēnapativaśananu peṭe mō
<lb n="10" break="no"/>dalu 50 I<unclear>ta</unclear>ni kuḍujītanaku<note n="440-2">Space for 5 letters isku.</note>vuṭṭaṁḍu kṣētramu ko
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nipeṭṭi I kṣētramu bhujiṁci Itaḍu bhaṁḍaranaku nelanu Eddumu kuṁca
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ḍa 7 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> ĀcaṁdrarkastaIganu peṭṭakaṁganu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> I darmmamu śrīvaiṣṇa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ma rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatru<unclear>ṇāpi</unclear> kṛtō darmmaḥ pālanīyō manīṣibhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatrōrē
<lb n="14" break="no"/>va hi śatrusyāddhammaḥ śatrurnna kasyacit <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī śrī śrī
</p>

